shultz invited professors edward said of columbia university and ibrahim abu lughud to visit him at the state department
israeli officials had reacted angrily to the meeting, saying it violated a u.s. commitment not to talk to the plo. said and lughud belong to the palestine national council, the plo's parliament-in-exile
